SQL> /*
DOC>Create and Rebuild various sequences.
DOC>
DOC>Note that the sequence usually shares the same name as the column(s) that it will be used to populate. This makes
DOC>it possible to write a meta data query that searches for values > the CURRVAL of a given sequence.
DOC>
DOC>*/
